  "description": "Extensions and Alterations to a mid-terrace property including: lowering the basement floor to form a habitable room; Construction of front and rear light wells including stairs and metal railings; demolition of the existing bay window to the rear kitchen and constructing a new bay window; forming a new loft extension with 4 conservation style rooflight to the front roof slope, enlarging the kitchen, bathroom and television room rear facing windows; a new conservation style rooflight to the rear 2-storey projection; Replacement timber framed, double glazed sash windows to match existing.",
